name: LA FRAISE ROSE
address: 481 W 6th Ave, Vancouver, BC V5Y 1L3, Canada

hasMenuItem.name: Classic Pink Box 🍓💖
hasMenuItem.description: Indulge in the sweet elegance of La Fraise Rose's Classic Pink Chocolate Box 🍓💖. Each strawberry is dipped in luscious pink chocolate, perfectly balanced between creamy richness and fruity freshness. A delightful treat that’s as beautiful as it is delicious, made to impress and satisfy ✨🍫.

hasMenuItem.name: Classic Milk Chocolate Box 🍓🍫
hasMenuItem.description: Indulge in pure bliss with La Fraise Rose’s Classic Milk Box 🍓🍫. Our premium milk chocolate-dipped strawberries are handpicked for freshness and decadently coated for a perfect bite every time. Juicy, sweet, and oh-so-smooth, each berry is a delightful treat that melts in your mouth!

hasMenuItem.name: Classic White Chocolate Box 🍓✨
hasMenuItem.description: Indulge in the La Fraise Rose Classic White Box 🍓✨ – a delightful assortment of hand-dipped, premium strawberries, perfectly coated in smooth white chocolate. Each bite is a heavenly blend of juicy sweetness and creamy decadence, making it the ultimate treat for any occasion! 🍫🤍

hasMenuItem.name: Dark Chocolate 🍓🍫
hasMenuItem.description: Indulge in our Classic Dark Chocolate Box 🍓🍫—featuring luscious, hand-dipped strawberries coated in rich, velvety dark chocolate. Each bite offers a perfect balance of sweet and bitter, with juicy, ripe strawberries at the heart of this decadent treat. Pure chocolate bliss in every bite! ✨

hasMenuItem.name: Elegant Box 🍓🍫
hasMenuItem.description: Indulge in the La Fraise Rose Elegant Chocolate Box 🍓🍫—a luxurious treat featuring handpicked, juicy strawberries dipped in rich, velvety chocolate. Perfectly balanced flavors with a delicate crunch in every bite, it's a decadent delight made for special moments and indulgence.

hasMenuItem.name: Fruit & Nut Box 🥜🍇
hasMenuItem.description: Indulge in the decadent Fruit & Nut Chocolate Box from La Fraise Rose 🍓🍫. Each piece combines juicy, hand-selected fruits and premium nuts, all dipped in rich, velvety chocolate for an irresistible treat. Perfect for those who crave a balance of sweet, tart, and crunchy goodness! 🥜🍇
